---
title: Chorizo Burgers with Aioli and a Green Salad
description: Calling all carnivores: our chefs doubled down on the meat in these hamburger patties, weaving cubes of chorizo into the ground beef. In other words, that’s meat mixed with more meat—need we say more? Well, we do have to let everyone know about the accents that give this dish some tasty, Spanish-style flair, like a smoked paprika aioli and a sherry vinegar–dressed salad.
